## Implementation Details (Current)

### Onboarding
- Progress record has `onboardingSeen`; community `tappalkaSettings.onboardingText` is optional. **tRPC:** `tappalka.markOnboardingSeen` sets onboarding for `(userId, communityId)`. Frontend uses onboarding flow and `progress.onboardingSeen`.

### Notifications
- When show-cost deduction leaves remainder after the investment pool, author may receive `investment_pool_depleted` (pool depleted; shows continue from rating/wallet/entity wallet per rules).
- When a post exits tappalka (e.g. `noAuthorWalletSpend`, or insufficient funds including source `CommunityWallet` for `sourceEntityId` posts), author may receive the same notification type with an “exited tappalka” style message.

